# Twilio Video Processors runtime assets — copied into public/ by
# scripts/copy-twilio-video-processors-assets.mjs (postinstall).
# The bytes change with the package version pinned in package.json /
# package-lock.json; checking them in would bloat history with
# multi-MB WASM/TFLite files on every bump. Per Sub-batch C task-video-C2.
public/twilio-video-processors-assets/
